<mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/10/Gastro-researcher-WF3829116_0189-16-x-9.jpg</mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>
