		<title>New genomic test could spare some people with melanoma from lymph node biopsy surgery&nbsp;</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/new-genomic-test-could-spare-some-people-with-melanoma-from-lymph-node-biopsy-surgery/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Susan Murphy]]></dc:creator>
